data.description: Make this lovely and charming  2 bd, 2 bath apartment your next home! Located in an active adult 55+ community with many amenities. Updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets. In-unit washer and dryer. Covered screen patio. Located just minutes from shops, restaurants and much more. One assigned parking space and an abundance of guest parking.
